{"type":"text","timestamp":1775849177382,"sessionID":"ses_2872b5c06ffeMNcifE3NGwSW9i","part":{"id":"prt_d78dbc36100123OXx7u4XzVAjR","messageID":"msg_d78db34320018DsjoLDCF886eD","sessionID":"ses_2872b5c06ffeMNcifE3NGwSW9i","type":"text","text":"I've created a comprehensive `design.md` file for AR-006 - Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management. The document includes:\n\n**Key Sections:**\n1. **Architecture** - High-level design with ASCII diagrams showing component interactions\n2. **Directory Structure** - Proposed file organization under `pkg/workloadmanager/`\n3. **Data Structures** - Complete Go type definitions for:\n   - Request/Response DTOs (`DeleteSandboxRequest`, `BatchDeleteRequest`, etc.)\n   - Lifecycle states and events\n   - Internal types (`LifecycleManager`, `ShutdownManager`, `ResourceCleaner`)\n   - Background worker configurations\n   - Constants for timeouts and error codes\n\n4. **API Contracts** - Detailed REST endpoints:\n   - `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId`\n   - `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId`\n   - `DELETE /v1/sandboxes` (batch)\n   - `POST /v1/sandboxes/:sessionId/terminate` (force)\n   - `GET /v1/sandboxes/:sessionId/lifecycle`\n\n5. **Error Handling** - Comprehensive error codes, sentinel errors, and handling patterns with retry logic\n\n6. **Testing Strategy** - Unit tests, integration tests, coverage targets, and test file organization\n\n**Design Highlights:**\n- Integrates with client-go library for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD access\n- Uses dynamic client for Sandbox/SandboxClaim CRD operations\n- Graceful shutdown with configurable timeout and automatic fallback\n- Parallel batch deletion with semaphore-based concurrency control\n- Background workers for idle detection and orphan cleanup\n- State machine for lifecycle tracking\n- Idempotent delete operations\n\nThe document follows the style of AR-005's design.md and incorporates all requirements from AR-006's delta-spec.md.","time":{"start":1775849177380,"end":1775849177380}}}
